{"tid":2112802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（指控中共？）日本：某些國家利用疫情去稱霸全球","createTime":"2020-07-17T15:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T18:10:43.000Z","uid":134071,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8522f4a13b757101b3be128dc17f4bfa602e1dde","tid":2112802,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"日本發表新版防衛白皮書 指控中國企圖改變現狀<br />\n最後更新：2020/07/14 11:44<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者楊明珠東京14日專電）日本防衛大臣河野太郎今天在內閣會議報告2020年版防衛白皮書內容。報告指出，武漢肺炎疫情蔓延全球，中國等國家為營造利己的國際秩序，使得國家間戰略競爭趨於明顯，中國也在釣魚台海域執拗地企圖片面改變現狀。<br />\n。。<br />\n白皮書也提及，有人指出中國等國家對於疫情蔓延的國家積極提供醫療專家的派遣、捐贈醫療物資，同時進行各種宣傳工作，但也趁疫情擴大引起社會不安和混亂之際發布假消息。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>內容指出，在疫情擴大之際，有些國家企圖營造利己的國際秩序或地區秩序，擴大影響力，導致國家間的戰略競爭趨於明顯，就安全保障上的課題而言，有必要予以高度關注。</strong>（編輯：陳惠珍）1090714<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/firstnews/202007140059.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202007140059.aspx&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=46436a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cna.com.tw/amp/news/firstnews/202007140059.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"f5c9de8bf081b4ec5b88756085e5ca4f7e98d5c0","tid":2112802,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1f231320f5d0995e50473536d7f19e449ae3e3","tid":2112802,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067493c23b382c0f23b8cc921c3f7cfec9769fc9","tid":2112802,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bdhcw-XmpGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dbdhcw-Xmp